Class DelimitedString

java.lang.Object
  tmiranda.mus.DelimitedString

public class DelimitedString
extends java.lang.Object

DelimitedString is a class that allows manipulation of Strings containing data separated by a delimiter.

public static void addToUserRecord(java.lang.Object Record,
                                   java.lang.String Flag,
                                   java.lang.String User)
Adds User to the delimited String contained in the User Record.

Parameters:
Record - A User Record from the UserRecordAPI.
Flag - The name of the Flag to store the data.
User - The User name to add to the Flag in the Record. The User name does not have to be a valid User so this method can really be used to add any data to a Flag.
